{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Welcome to Thailand."},{"time":3000,"text":"Now, when I was a young man -- 40 years ago,"},{"time":6000,"text":"the country was very, very poor"},{"time":8000,"text":"with lots and lots and lots of people living in poverty."},{"time":11000,"text":"We decided to do something about it,"},{"time":14000,"text":"but we didn't begin with a welfare program"},{"time":16000,"text":"or a poverty reduction program."},{"time":19000,"text":"But we began with a family-planning program,"},{"time":22000,"text":"following a very successful"},{"time":24000,"text":"maternal child health activity,"},{"time":26000,"text":"sets of activities."},{"time":28000,"text":"So basically, no one would accept family planning"},{"time":31000,"text":"if their children didn't survive."},{"time":33000,"text":"So the first step: get to the children, get to the mothers,"},{"time":36000,"text":"and then follow up with family planning."},{"time":38000,"text":"Not just child mortality alone, you need also family planning."},{"time":41000,"text":"Now let me take you back"},{"time":43000,"text":"as to why we needed to do it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45000,"text":"In my country, that was the case in 1974."},{"time":48000,"text":"Seven children per family --"},{"time":50000,"text":"tremendous growth at 3.3 percent."},{"time":52000,"text":"There was just no future."},{"time":54000,"text":"We needed to reduce the population growth rate."},{"time":56000,"text":"So we said, \"Let's do it.\""},{"time":58000,"text":"The women said, \"We agree. We'll use pills,"},{"time":60000,"text":"but we need a doctor to prescribe the pills,\""},{"time":63000,"text":"and we had very, very few doctors."},{"time":65000,"text":"We didn't take no as an answer;"},{"time":67000,"text":"we took no as a question."},{"time":69000,"text":"We went to the nurses and the midwives, who were also women,"},{"time":72000,"text":"and did a fantastic job"},{"time":74000,"text":"at explaining how to use the pill."},{"time":76000,"text":"That was wonderful,"},{"time":78000,"text":"but it covered only 20 percent of the country."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80000,"text":"What do we do for the other 80 percent --"},{"time":82000,"text":"leave them alone and say, \"Well, they're not medical personnel.\""},{"time":85000,"text":"No, we decided to do a bit more."},{"time":87000,"text":"So we went to the ordinary people that you saw."},{"time":90000,"text":"Actually, below that yellow sign --"},{"time":92000,"text":"I wish they hadn't wiped that,"},{"time":94000,"text":"because there was \"Coca-Cola\" there."},{"time":97000,"text":"We were so much bigger than Coca-Cola in those days."},{"time":100000,"text":"And no difference,"},{"time":102000,"text":"the people they chose were the people we chose."},{"time":105000,"text":"They were well-known in the community,"},{"time":107000,"text":"they knew that customers were always right,"},{"time":109000,"text":"and they were terrific, and they practiced their family planning themselves."},{"time":112000,"text":"So they could supply pills and condoms"},{"time":114000,"text":"throughout the country, in every village of the country."},{"time":116000,"text":"So there we are. We went to the people"},{"time":118000,"text":"who were seen as the cause of the problem"},{"time":120000,"text":"to be the solution."},{"time":122000,"text":"Wherever there were people --"},{"time":124000,"text":"and you can see boats with the women, selling things --"},{"time":126000,"text":"here's the floating market"},{"time":128000,"text":"selling bananas and crabs"},{"time":130000,"text":"and also contraceptives --"},{"time":132000,"text":"wherever you find people,"},{"time":134000,"text":"you'll find contraceptives in Thailand."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136000,"text":"And then we decided, why not get to religion"},{"time":138000,"text":"because in the Philippines,"},{"time":140000,"text":"the Catholic Church was pretty strong,"},{"time":142000,"text":"and Thai people were Buddhist."},{"time":144000,"text":"We went to them and they said, \"Look, could you help us?\""},{"time":146000,"text":"I'm there -- the one in blue, not the yellow --"},{"time":149000,"text":"holding a bowl of holy water"},{"time":151000,"text":"for the monk to sprinkle holy water"},{"time":153000,"text":"on pills and condoms"},{"time":155000,"text":"for the sanctity of the family."},{"time":158000,"text":"And this picture was sent throughout the country."},{"time":160000,"text":"So some of the monks in the villages were doing the same thing themselves."},{"time":163000,"text":"And the women were saying, \"No wonder we have no side-effects."},{"time":166000,"text":"It's been blessed.\""},{"time":168000,"text":"That was their perception."}]},{"cues":[{"time":170000,"text":"And then we went to teachers."},{"time":172000,"text":"You need everybody to be involved"},{"time":175000,"text":"in trying to provide whatever it is"},{"time":178000,"text":"that make humanity a better place."},{"time":180000,"text":"So we went to the teachers."},{"time":182000,"text":"Over a quarter of a million were taught about family planning"},{"time":184000,"text":"with a new alphabet -- A, B for birth, C for condom,"},{"time":187000,"text":"I for IUD, V for vasectomy."},{"time":189000,"text":"And then we had a snakes and ladders game, where you throw dice."},{"time":191000,"text":"If you land on anything pro-family planning, you move ahead."},{"time":194000,"text":"Like, \"Mother takes the pill every night."},{"time":196000,"text":"Very good, mother. Move ahead."},{"time":198000,"text":"Uncle buys a condom. Very good, uncle. Move ahead."},{"time":200000,"text":"Uncle gets drunk, doesn't use condom. Come back, start again.\""},{"time":202000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":204000,"text":"Again, education, class entertainment."},{"time":207000,"text":"And the kids were doing it in school too."},{"time":209000,"text":"We had relay races with condoms,"},{"time":211000,"text":"we had children's condom-blowing championship."},{"time":213000,"text":"And before long,"},{"time":215000,"text":"the condom was know as the girl's best friend."},{"time":218000,"text":"In Thailand, for poor people, diamonds don't make it --"},{"time":220000,"text":"so the condom is the girl's best friend."}]},{"cues":[{"time":224000,"text":"We introduced our first microcredit program in 1975,"},{"time":227000,"text":"and the women who organized it said,"},{"time":229000,"text":"\"We only want to lend"},{"time":231000,"text":"to women who practice family planning."},{"time":233000,"text":"If you're pregnant, take care of your pregnancy."},{"time":235000,"text":"If you're not pregnant, you can take a loan out from us.\""},{"time":237000,"text":"And that was run by them."},{"time":239000,"text":"And after 35/36 years,"},{"time":241000,"text":"it's still going on."},{"time":243000,"text":"It's a part of the Village Development Bank;"},{"time":245000,"text":"it's not a real bank, but it's a fund -- microcredit."},{"time":248000,"text":"And we didn't need a big organization to run it --"},{"time":250000,"text":"it was run by the villagers themselves."},{"time":252000,"text":"And you probably hardly see a Thai man there,"},{"time":254000,"text":"it's always women, women, women, women."},{"time":257000,"text":"And then we thought we'd help America,"},{"time":259000,"text":"because America's been helping everyone,"},{"time":261000,"text":"whether they want help or not."},{"time":263000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":268000,"text":"And this is on the Fourth of July."},{"time":271000,"text":"We decided to provide vasectomy to all men,"},{"time":274000,"text":"but in particular, American men to the front of the queue,"},{"time":276000,"text":"right up to the Ambassador's residence"},{"time":278000,"text":"during his [unclear]."},{"time":280000,"text":"And the hotel gave us the ballroom for it --"},{"time":282000,"text":"very appropriate room."},{"time":284000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":287000,"text":"And since it was near lunch time,"},{"time":289000,"text":"they said, \"All right, we'll give you some lunch."},{"time":291000,"text":"Of course, it must be American cola."},{"time":293000,"text":"You get two brands, Coke and Pepsi."},{"time":295000,"text":"And then the food is either hamburger or hotdog.\""},{"time":298000,"text":"And I thought a hotdog will be more symbolic."},{"time":300000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":302000,"text":"And here is this, then, young man called Willy Bohm"},{"time":305000,"text":"who worked for the USAID."},{"time":307000,"text":"Obviously, he's had his vasectomy"},{"time":309000,"text":"because his hotdog is half eaten, and he was very happy."},{"time":312000,"text":"It made a lot of news in America, and it angered some people also."},{"time":315000,"text":"I said, \"Don't worry. Come over and I'll do the whole lot of you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":317000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":319000,"text":"And what happened?"},{"time":321000,"text":"In all this thing,"},{"time":323000,"text":"from seven children to 1.5 children,"},{"time":325000,"text":"population growth rate of 3.3 to 0.5."},{"time":328000,"text":"You could call it the Coca-Cola approach if you like --"},{"time":331000,"text":"it was exactly the same thing."},{"time":333000,"text":"I'm not sure whether Coca-Cola followed us, or we followed Coca-Cola,"},{"time":336000,"text":"but we're good friends."},{"time":338000,"text":"And so that's the case of everyone joining in."},{"time":340000,"text":"We didn't have a strong government. We didn't have lots of doctors."},{"time":343000,"text":"But it's everybody's job"},{"time":345000,"text":"who can change attitude and behavior."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347000,"text":"Then AIDS came along and hit Thailand,"},{"time":349000,"text":"and we had to stop doing a lot of good things"},{"time":351000,"text":"to fight AIDS."},{"time":353000,"text":"But unfortunately, the government was in denial, denial, denial."},{"time":356000,"text":"So our work wasn't affected."},{"time":358000,"text":"So I thought, \"Well, if you can't go to the government, go to the military.\""},{"time":361000,"text":"So I went to the military"},{"time":363000,"text":"and asked to borrow 300 radio stations."},{"time":365000,"text":"They have more than the government,"},{"time":367000,"text":"and they've got more guns than the government."},{"time":369000,"text":"So I asked them, could they help us"},{"time":371000,"text":"in our fight against HIV."},{"time":373000,"text":"And after I gave them statistics,"},{"time":375000,"text":"they said, \"Yes. Okay. You can use all the radio stations, television stations.\""},{"time":378000,"text":"And that's when we went onto the airwaves."},{"time":381000,"text":"And then we got a new prime minister soon after that."},{"time":383000,"text":"And he said, \"Mechai, could you come and join?\""},{"time":386000,"text":"He asked me in because he liked my wife a lot."},{"time":388000,"text":"So I said, \"Okay.\""},{"time":390000,"text":"He became the chairman of the National AIDS Committee"},{"time":392000,"text":"and increased the budget fifty-fold."}]},{"cues":[{"time":394000,"text":"Every ministry, even judges, had to be involved in AIDS education --"},{"time":397000,"text":"everyone -- and we said the public, institutions,"},{"time":400000,"text":"religious institutions, schools --"},{"time":402000,"text":"everyone was involved."},{"time":404000,"text":"And here, every media person"},{"time":406000,"text":"had to be trained for HIV."},{"time":408000,"text":"And we gave every station half a minute extra"},{"time":411000,"text":"for advertising to earn more money."},{"time":414000,"text":"So they were happy with that."},{"time":416000,"text":"And then AIDS education in all schools,"},{"time":418000,"text":"starting from university."},{"time":420000,"text":"And these are high school kids teaching high school kids."},{"time":423000,"text":"And the best teachers were the girls, not the boys,"},{"time":425000,"text":"and they were terrific."},{"time":427000,"text":"And these girls who go around teaching about safe sex and HIV"},{"time":430000,"text":"were known as Mother Theresa."},{"time":433000,"text":"And then we went down one more step."},{"time":435000,"text":"These are primary school kids -- third, fourth grade --"},{"time":437000,"text":"going to every household in the village,"},{"time":439000,"text":"every household in the whole of Thailand,"},{"time":441000,"text":"giving AIDS information and a condom"},{"time":443000,"text":"to every household,"},{"time":445000,"text":"given by these young kids."},{"time":447000,"text":"And no parents objected, because we were trying to save lives,"},{"time":450000,"text":"and this was a lifesaver."},{"time":453000,"text":"And we said, \"Everyone needs to be involved.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":455000,"text":"So you have the companies also realizing"},{"time":457000,"text":"that sick staff don't work, and dead customers don't buy."},{"time":459000,"text":"So they all trained."},{"time":461000,"text":"And then we have this Captain Condom,"},{"time":463000,"text":"with his Harvard MBA,"},{"time":465000,"text":"going to schools and night spots."},{"time":467000,"text":"And they loved him. You need a symbol of something."},{"time":470000,"text":"In every country, every program, you need a symbol,"},{"time":473000,"text":"and this is probably the best thing he's ever done with his MBA."},{"time":476000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":479000,"text":"And then we gave condoms out everywhere on the streets --"},{"time":481000,"text":"everywhere, everywhere."},{"time":483000,"text":"In taxis, you get condoms."},{"time":485000,"text":"And also, in traffic,"},{"time":487000,"text":"the policemen give you condoms -- our \"cops and rubbers\" programs."},{"time":490000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":493000,"text":"So, can you imagine New York policemen giving out condoms?"},{"time":496000,"text":"Of course I can. And they'd enjoy it immensely;"},{"time":499000,"text":"I see them standing around right now, everywhere."},{"time":501000,"text":"Imagine if they had condoms,"},{"time":503000,"text":"giving out to all sorts of people."},{"time":505000,"text":"And then, new change,"},{"time":507000,"text":"we had hair bands, clothing"},{"time":509000,"text":"and the condom for your mobile phone"},{"time":511000,"text":"during the rainy season."}]},{"cues":[{"time":513000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":515000,"text":"And these were the condoms that we introduced."},{"time":520000,"text":"One says, \"Weapon of mass protection.\""},{"time":522000,"text":"We found --"},{"time":524000,"text":"you know -- somebody here was searching for the weapon of mass destruction,"},{"time":527000,"text":"but we have found the weapon of mass protection: the condom."},{"time":530000,"text":"And then it says here, with the American flag,"},{"time":532000,"text":"\"Don't leave home without it.\""},{"time":534000,"text":"But I have some to give out afterward."},{"time":537000,"text":"But let me warn you, these are Thai-sized,"},{"time":539000,"text":"so be very careful."},{"time":541000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":543000,"text":"And so you can see"},{"time":545000,"text":"that condoms can do so many things."},{"time":548000,"text":"Look at this --"},{"time":550000,"text":"I gave this to Al Gore and to Bill Senior also."},{"time":553000,"text":"Stop global warming; use condoms."},{"time":557000,"text":"And then this is the picture I mentioned to you --"},{"time":560000,"text":"the weapon of mass protection."},{"time":563000,"text":"And let the next Olympics save some lives."},{"time":566000,"text":"Why just run around?"},{"time":568000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":571000,"text":"And then finally,"},{"time":573000,"text":"in Thailand we're Buddhist, we don't have a God,"},{"time":576000,"text":"so instead, we say, \"In rubber we trust.\""},{"time":578000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":580000,"text":"So you can see that we added everything to our endeavor"},{"time":582000,"text":"to make life better for the people."},{"time":584000,"text":"We had condoms in all the refrigerators in the hotels and the schools,"},{"time":587000,"text":"because alcohol impairs judgment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":589000,"text":"And then what happened?"},{"time":591000,"text":"After all this time, everybody joined in."},{"time":594000,"text":"According to the U.N.,"},{"time":595000,"text":"new cases of HIV"},{"time":597000,"text":"declined by 90 percent,"},{"time":599000,"text":"and according to the World Bank,"},{"time":601000,"text":"7.7 million lives were saved."},{"time":603000,"text":"Otherwise there wouldn't be many Thais walking around today."},{"time":606000,"text":"So it just showed you, you could do something about it."},{"time":609000,"text":"90 percent of the funding came from Thailand."},{"time":611000,"text":"There was political commitment, some financial commitment,"},{"time":614000,"text":"and everybody joined in the fight."},{"time":616000,"text":"So just don't leave it to the specialists and doctors and nurses."},{"time":619000,"text":"We all need to help."}]},{"cues":[{"time":621000,"text":"And then we decided to help people out of poverty,"},{"time":623000,"text":"now that we got AIDS somewhat out of the way --"},{"time":625000,"text":"this time, not with government alone,"},{"time":627000,"text":"but in cooperation with the business community."},{"time":630000,"text":"Because poor people are business people"},{"time":632000,"text":"who lack business skills and access to credit."},{"time":635000,"text":"Those are the things to be provided by the business community."},{"time":638000,"text":"We're trying to turn them into barefoot entrepreneurs,"},{"time":641000,"text":"little business people."},{"time":643000,"text":"The only way out of poverty is through business enterprise."},{"time":645000,"text":"So, that was done."},{"time":647000,"text":"The money goes from the company into the village"},{"time":649000,"text":"via tree-planting."},{"time":651000,"text":"It's not a free gift."},{"time":653000,"text":"They plant the trees, and the money goes into their microcredit fund,"},{"time":655000,"text":"which we call the Village Development Bank."},{"time":657000,"text":"Everybody joins in,"},{"time":659000,"text":"and they feel they own the bank,"},{"time":661000,"text":"because they have brought the money in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":663000,"text":"And before you can borrow the money, you need to be trained."},{"time":666000,"text":"And we believe if you want to help the poor,"},{"time":668000,"text":"those who are living in poverty,"},{"time":670000,"text":"access to credit must be a human right."},{"time":673000,"text":"Access to credit must be a human right."},{"time":675000,"text":"Otherwise they'll never get out of poverty."},{"time":678000,"text":"And then before getting a loan, you must be trained."},{"time":680000,"text":"Here's what we call a \"barefoot MBA,\""},{"time":682000,"text":"teaching people how to do business"},{"time":684000,"text":"so that, when they borrow money, they'll succeed with the business."},{"time":687000,"text":"These are some of the businesses:"},{"time":689000,"text":"mushrooms, crabs, vegetables,"},{"time":692000,"text":"trees, fruits,"},{"time":694000,"text":"and this is very interesting -- Nike ice cream and Nike biscuits;"},{"time":697000,"text":"this is a village sponsored by Nike."},{"time":699000,"text":"They said, \"They should stop making shoes and clothes."},{"time":701000,"text":"Make these better, because we can afford them.\""},{"time":705000,"text":"And then we have silk, Thai silk."},{"time":707000,"text":"Now we're making Scottish tartans, as you can see on the left,"},{"time":710000,"text":"to sell to all people of Scottish ancestors."},{"time":713000,"text":"So anyone sitting in and watching TV,"},{"time":715000,"text":"get in touch with me."},{"time":717000,"text":"And then this is our answer to Starbucks in Thailand --"},{"time":720000,"text":"\"Coffee and Condoms.\""},{"time":722000,"text":"See, Starbucks you awake, we keep you awake and alive."},{"time":725000,"text":"That's the difference."},{"time":727000,"text":"Can you imagine, at every Starbucks"},{"time":729000,"text":"that you can also get condoms?"},{"time":731000,"text":"You can order your condoms with your with your cappuccino."}]},{"cues":[{"time":736000,"text":"And then now, finally in education,"},{"time":738000,"text":"we want to change the school as being underutilized"},{"time":741000,"text":"into a place where it's a lifelong learning center for everyone."},{"time":745000,"text":"We call this our School-Based Integrated Rural Development."},{"time":748000,"text":"And it's a center, a focal point"},{"time":750000,"text":"for economic and social development."},{"time":752000,"text":"Re-do the school,"},{"time":754000,"text":"make it serve the community needs."},{"time":757000,"text":"And here is a bamboo building --"},{"time":759000,"text":"all of them are bamboo."},{"time":761000,"text":"This is a geodesic dome made of bamboo."},{"time":764000,"text":"And I'm sure Buckminster Fuller would be very, very proud"},{"time":767000,"text":"to see a bamboo geodesic dome."},{"time":770000,"text":"And we use vegetables around the school ground,"},{"time":772000,"text":"so they raise their own vegetables."}]},{"cues":[{"time":774000,"text":"And then, finally, I firmly believe,"},{"time":777000,"text":"if we want the MDGs to work --"},{"time":779000,"text":"the Millennium Development Goals --"},{"time":781000,"text":"we need to add family planning to it."},{"time":783000,"text":"Of course, child mortality first and then family planning --"},{"time":786000,"text":"everyone needs family planning service --"},{"time":788000,"text":"it's underutilized."},{"time":790000,"text":"So we have now found the weapon of mass protection."},{"time":792000,"text":"And we also ask the next Olympics"},{"time":794000,"text":"to be involved in saving lives."},{"time":797000,"text":"And then, finally, that is our network."},{"time":800000,"text":"And these are our Thai tulips."}]},{"cues":[{"time":803000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":805000,"text":"Thank you very much indeed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":807000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}